page.title: 12CLUBS
page.content:
I belong to three different organizations,they are;Guides,Questers,and the Bournemouth Music Centre.
The Guides I belong to is the 20th Bournemouth. Our meeting place is at Eastcliff Church next to 2CR Radio Station. I have been a Guide for three months.
Questers is a Church Youth Club. It meets on Tuesday evenings at 7.30pm until 9.00pm. The Youth Club is for people aged between 9 and 14 years old. Each week we attend a different place for an organized event.
The Bournemouth Music Centre is a group of young musicians who have their grade 3 exam. Linda Brown - 1B2
